buildingOrderModule.scoringDirector

Interface ScoreGeneratorFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ScoreGeneratorFactoryTerranBio, ScoreGeneratorFactoryTerranDefault, ScoreGeneratorFactoryTerranMachines

    public interface ScoreGeneratorFactory
    ScoreGeneratorFactory.java --- A Interface defining a factory for ScoreGenerators (Abstract Factory Pattern).
    Note:
    The objects returned by this factory must only be generated once for any factory that relies on storing information!
    Author:
    P H - 16.07.2017
